Detail:

<strong>Professional Description:</strong>

&nbsp;

<strong>Enhance your photography, live streaming, and video production with this 210cm Adjustable Tripod Stand designed for ring lights, cameras, and studio equipment. Built with durable metal materials, this stand combines strength, stability, and portability for professional and everyday use.</strong>

&nbsp;

<strong>Key Features:</strong>

&nbsp;

<strong>Adjustable Height (Up to 210cm): Scalable design allows you to set the perfect height for portraits, product photography, or live video sessions.</strong>

&nbsp;

<strong>Stylish Painted Finish: Smooth surface with an elegant look, ensuring both durability and a professional appearance.</strong>

&nbsp;

<strong>Universal 1/4" Screw Mount: Compatible with most ring lights, cameras, and standard studio equipment.</strong>

&nbsp;

<strong>Durable Metal Build: Made from high-quality, long-lasting metal materials for reliable performance.</strong>

&nbsp;

<strong>Foldable &amp; Portable: Easy to collapse and store, making it convenient for travel and studio organization.</strong>

&nbsp;

<strong>Note: Manual measurements may have slight deviations, but this does not affect functionality.</strong>
